criteria.driver_alignment:
Define — stated financial objective, hurdle rate, project parameters before implementation;  
Discover — framed the capital-budgeting goal and key inputs (asset life, cost structure);  
Represent — mapped a standard free-cash-flow model prior to coding;  
Implement — ran Python code and showed outputs;  
Validate — manually calculated year‑1 to confirm model;  
Evolve — performed sensitivity/stress tests revealing downside risk;  
Reflect — synthesized recommendation, quantified value creation, and issued risk-based caveats.
